  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Both PORT and DIO is of Type 3"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Type III = 1b + 2b + 3b"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "PORT"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "The PORT driver supports the multicore concept. All the APIs except Port_Init can be accessed from any core. The Port_Init API needs to be called only once from any core"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "DIO"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "The DIO driver supports the multicore functionality. The DIO driver service can be accessed from any core"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Architecture overview"
    },
